      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Static Sites Are Awesome&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/images/static-sites.jpg&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Static sites are &lt;strong&gt;fast, secure, and scalable&lt;/strong&gt;. Here is why:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Speed&lt;/strong&gt;: No database queries, just static files.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security&lt;/strong&gt;: No server-side vulnerabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cost&lt;/strong&gt;: Host them for free on platforms like GitHub Pages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Static sites are the future! - &amp;quot; &lt;a href=&#34;https://example.com&#34;&gt;Web Dev Weekly&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
